{
  "stem": "27507.10",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was not-- the street was really some distance away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You had to walk about 100 meters to come to the street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was a bit like in the country in a way, although it was, as I said, pretty much in the center of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the wife of Koper, Marta, she was on the whole a peasant.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She was a peasant woman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She looked like a peasant woman, with big red cheeks, and quite a sturdy woman.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She must have there in her forties, no children, and very strong, and strongly built, and working in the garden.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That was her favorite place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She had, as well, another place in the country near Warsaw, about 10 kilometers-- no 20 kilometers-- from Warsaw, where they had a tiny little house, and allotment.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they were going there to plant-- to look after the orchard, and the garden, and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she was really-- she came from the country.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She was a peasant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And, suddenly, here she was-- her husband was a petty official.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And, suddenly, God knows why exactly, because they never were particularly, one would have thought inclined or interested, they suddenly got into this business of keeping Jews, saving Jews.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "In the beginning, it must have been purely Koper to earn some money, in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And, somehow, he got involved in that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And somehow, suddenly, those Jews were human beings.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they didn't feel like throwing anybody out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And though in the beginning people paid them to be there-- I mean Hania probably paid them and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Later, they finished up with quite a lot of people who didn't have any money.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they kept them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They even bought food for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
